Carol Vorderman shared a series of flirty snaps to her 227,000 Instagram followers on Friday from the pilot’s seat of a plane. The 61-year-old wore her usual figure-hugging workout wear and teased that she “had to try on the captain’s hat”. She wrote in the caption: “Had such a laugh having an entire aeroplane as my dressing room to shoot a new commercial today. “Had to try on the Captain's hat tho....Suits me?” (sic) Dozens of her followers took to the comments to praise the former Countdown star. Paul gushed: “Hello gorgeous girl. In your element there.” While Stephen echoed: “Looking lovely!” And Jason praised: “Stunning.” Carol is set to appear on Celebrity Gogglebox on Friday at 9pm on Channel 4.